            <p>= e<sup>&minus;(S<sub>c</sub> + S<sub>q</sub>)</sup></p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-faint)] mt-4">
            Log-space: additive (engineering). Real-space: multiplicative (theoretical). Same equation, different views.
