          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] mb-2">Analogy 2: I0 as Holographic Boundary</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">BCIs already work holographically: EEG/ECoG measure surface potentials, and source localization reconstructs 3D brain activity from 2D surface measurements. However, the holographic principle operates at Planck-scale physics &mdash; applying it to a macroscopic electrode 30 orders of magnitude larger is not formally justified.</p>
