          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] mb-2">Analogy 3: Key Exchange as Page Curve</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Without the session key, accumulated ciphertext reveals nothing. With the key, all frames decode. The key is the analog of the Page time <a href="#ref-68">[68]</a>. The visual similarity is genuine, but the underlying mechanisms are different.</p>
