            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Hawking radiation has a maximum entropy spectrum <a href="#ref-72">[72]</a>. AES-256-GCM ciphertext is computationally indistinguishable from random noise. The parallel is structural, not physical.</p>
          </div>
